<i>noun</i>: 신문 [신ː문], 문초 [문ː초] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>신문 [신ː문]</dt><br>
<dd>1. questioning</dd><br>
<dd>이미 알고 있는 일이 사실인지 거짓인지 확인하기 위하여 캐물음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of questioning inquisitively in order to confirm whether an already known fact is true or false.</dd><br>
<dd>2. interrogation</dd><br>
<dd>정확한 법적 판결을 위해 관계자를 상대로 사건에 대해 캐물으며 조사함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of questioning inquisitively and investigating people concerned regarding a certain incident for an accurate legal decision.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>문초 [문ː초]</dt><br>
<dd>questioning; investigation</dd><br>
<dd>잘못이 있는 사람에게 죄, 잘못 등을 따져 묻거나 심문함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of questioning or interrogating a guilty person about his/her wrongdoings or crimes.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>